targets.query: SELECT "mean_load_instant_power" FROM "http" WHERE $timeFilter tz('America/Los_Angeles')
SELECT mean(from_pw) - mean(to_pw) FROM autogen.http WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(5m) tz('America/Los_Angeles')
SELECT mean(from_grid) - mean(to_grid) FROM autogen.http WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(5m) tz('America/Los_Angeles')
SELECT "mean_percentage" FROM "http" WHERE $timeFilter

SELECT  (1+from_solar/abs(from_solar))*from_solar/2  FROM (SELECT integral(solar)/1000/3600 - integral(to_pw)/1000/3600 - integral(to_grid)/1000/3600  AS from_solar FROM autogen.http WHERE  $timeFilter tz('America/Los_Angeles'))

panels.title: Power Flow

targets.query: SELECT min("grid_status") FROM "grid"."http" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) tz('America/Los_Angeles')
SELECT integral("load_instant_power")  / 1000 / 3600 FROM "http" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1h) tz('America/Los_Angeles')
SELECT integral("solar_instant_power")  / 1000 / 3600 FROM "http" WHERE $timeFilter
SELECT integral("battery_instant_power")  / -1000 / 3600 FROM "http" WHERE ("battery_instant_power" <= 0) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1h) tz('America/Los_Angeles')
SELECT integral("battery_instant_power")  / 1000 / 3600 FROM "http" WHERE ("battery_instant_power" > 0) AND $timeFilter tz('America/Los_Angeles')
SELECT integral("site_instant_power",1m)  / -1000 / 3600 * 60 FROM "http" WHERE ("site_instant_power" < 0) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1h) tz('America/Los_Angeles')
SELECT integral("site_instant_power", 1m)  / 1000 / 3600 * 60 FROM "http" WHERE ("site_instant_power" > 0) AND $timeFilter
SELECT fp FROM (SELECT sum("from_pw")  * 0.19 AS fp FROM kwh.http WHERE  $timeFilter tz('America/Los_Angeles'))
SELECT s - (tp + tg) FROM (SELECT sum("solar") * 0.19 AS s,  sum("to_pw")  * 0.19 AS tp, sum("to_grid") * 0.19 AS tg FROM kwh.http WHERE  $timeFilter tz('America/Los_Angeles'))
SELECT tg FROM (SELECT sum("to_pw")  * 0.19 AS tp, sum("solar") * 0.19 AS s, sum("to_grid") * 0.19 AS tg FROM kwh.http WHERE  $timeFilter tz('America/Los_Angeles'))

SELECT tg + (s - tp - tg ) + fp FROM (SELECT sum("to_pw")  * 0.19 AS tp, sum("solar") * 0.19 AS s, sum("to_grid") * 0.19 AS tg, sum("from_pw") * 0.19 AS fp FROM kwh.http WHERE  $timeFilter tz('America/Los_Angeles'))

SELECT  (1+from_solar/abs(from_solar))*from_solar/2  FROM (SELECT integral(solar)/1000/3600 - integral(to_pw)/1000/3600 - integral(to_grid)/1000/3600  AS from_solar FROM autogen.http WHERE  $timeFilter tz('America/Los_Angeles'))

targets.query: SELECT last("load_instant_power")  / 1000 AS "Home", last("solar_instant_power")  / 1000 AS "Solar", last("battery_instant_power")  / 1000 AS "Battery", last("site_instant_power")  / 1000 AS "Grid" FROM "raw"."http" WHERE $timeFilter
SELECT sum("home") FROM "kwh"."http" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d) fill(0) tz('America/Los_Angeles')
SELECT sum("from_grid") FROM "daily"."http" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d) fill(0) tz('America/Los_Angeles')
SELECT sum("to_grid")  * -1 FROM "daily"."http" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d) fill(0) tz('America/Los_Angeles')
SELECT sum("solar") FROM "kwh"."http" WHERE ("solar" > 0) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d) fill(0) tz('America/Los_Angeles')
SELECT sum("solar") FROM "kwh"."http" WHERE ("solar" > 0) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d) fill(0) tz('America/Los_Angeles')
